-9b8a-460fdeb447a0" image48x27="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2023-12/the-red-shoes-1948-moira-shearer-red-shoes.jpg/96x54-cropped/the-red-shoes-1948-moira-shearer-red-shoes.jpg" standfirst="Highlights from our exhibition The Red Shoes: Behind the Mirror, including the ballet shoes worn by Moira Shearer and on loan from Martin Scorseses private collection." class="ArticleCard__Outer-sc-zrtbni-0 eIZIIS articleCard Features"><div class="ArticleCard__CategoryTag-sc-zrtbni-7 yMPPW">Features</div><div class="ArticleCard__PageImageContainer-sc-zrtbni-5 ehvIXQ"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImage-sc-zrtbni-6 iyvAqw image"></div></div><h3 class="ArticleCard__Heading-sc-zrtbni-3 bynrVe">The Red Shoes: Moira Shearers ballet shoes and other artefacts from the making of Powell and Pressburgers classic</h3><div class="ArticleCard__Meta-sc-zrtbni-1 edgoES"><p class="ArticleCard__Author-sc-zrtbni-2 KIAzD">By Claire Smith</p></div><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/features/red-shoes-moira-shearers-ballet-shoes-other-artefacts-from-making-powell-pressburgers-classic" title="Read The Red Shoes: Moira Shearers ballet shoes and other artefacts from the making of Powell and Pressburgers classic" class="ArticleCard__CallToAction-sc-zrtbni-4 fwpHHm"><span>The Red Shoes: Moira Shearers ballet shoes and other artefacts from the making of Powell and Pressburgers classic</span></a></article><article uuid="335e329a-8e1a-4bef-bf25-6ccde8e2142d" image48x27="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-09/the-red-shoes-1948-title-card.jpeg/96x54-cropped/the-red-shoes-1948-title-card.jpeg" standfirst="We remember some of the ingredients that make Powell and Pressburgers glorious dance classic The Red Shoes so special." class="ArticleCard__Outer-sc-zrtbni-0 eIZIIS articleCard Features"><div class="ArticleCard__CategoryTag-sc-zrtbni-7 yMPPW">Features</div><div class="ArticleCard__PageImageContainer-sc-zrtbni-5 ehvIXQ"><div clas