st film colour systems","url":"https://www.bfi.org.uk/lists/10-best-film-colour-systems","image":{"src":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-07/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg/960x540-cropped/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg","thumbnail":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-07/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg/960x540-cropped/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg","preload":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-07/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg/96x54-cropped/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg","sidebar":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-07/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg/480x720-cropped/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg","sidebarPreload":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-07/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg/48x72-cropped/the-red-shoes-1948-technicolor-iv-frame-moira-shearer-cropped.jpg","alt":null},"category":"","authors":["Uli Ruedel"],"type":"Lists","sourceCms":"core-cms","summary":"Do you know your Technicolor from your Kodachrome? The science of colour in film, which will be explored in a fourth annual event at BFI Southbank in March, has brought us many innovative systems over the past 120 years. Heres an experts guide to 10 of the best.","created":"2016-01-26T00:00:00.000Z"},{"uuid":"565f31e2-9ac1-46ff-b4a6-cf14a7cbaf69","title":"Let me grab your soul away  Kate Bush and gothic films","url":"https://www.bfi.org.uk/features/let-me-grab-your-soul-away-kate-bush-gothic-films","image":{"src":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/202